'''Nierenstein反应'''（Nierenstein reaction）

用[[重氮甲烷|重氮甲烷]]将[[酰氯|酰氯]]转化为[[卤代酮|卤代酮]]。<ref>{{cite journal en
 | author = Clibbens, D.; Nierenstein, M. 
 | title = The action of diazomethane on some aromatic acyl chlorides
 | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.|J. Chem. Soc.]]
 | year = 1915 
 | volume = 107 
 | pages = 1491
 | doi = 10.1039/CT9150701491}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en
 | author = [[Werner_Emmanuel_Bachmann|Bachman, W. E.]]; Struve, W. S. 
 | journal = Org. React. 
 | year = 1942 
 | volume = 1    
 | pages = 38 }}（综述）</ref>

<br />
[[Image:NierensteinReaction.png|center]]

==反应机理==
反应机理与[[Arndt-Eistert反应|Arndt-Eistert反应]]类似，即酰氯与重氮甲烷缩合为[[重氮酮|重氮酮]]中间体，然后重氮酮发生质子化、放出氮气得到产物。

<br />
[[Image:NierensteinMechanism.png|center]]
<br />

以[[苯乙酰氯|苯乙酰氯]]合成[[苄基氯甲基酮|苄基氯甲基酮]]时，需要通入氯化氢气体才能使重氮酮转化为卤代酮产物。<ref>McPhee, W. D; Klingsberg, E. ''[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]]'', Coll. Vol. 3, p.119 (1955); Vol. 26, p.13 (1946). ([http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0119.pdf Article] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0119.pdf |date=20110718031226 }})</ref>

